"{\"uid\": \"straitstimes.com-world-europe-bittersweet-olympic-experience-for-some-in-paris-suburb-home-of-games\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Choose edition  Search  singapore  asia  world  opinion  life  business  sport  Visual  Podcasts  SPH Rewards  STClassifieds  Paid press releases  Advertise with us  FAQs  Contact us  Sign up now:Get ST's newsletters delivered to your inbox  The Olympic Village that has been home to some 10,500 athletes will be transformed into housing units, including social and student housing.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.5217200619384247e-13, \"text\": \"SPH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"score\": 0.9604822703099307, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advertise\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\"}, {\"begin\": 246, \"end\": 261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.372229418665799e-24, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: REUTERS  PublishedAug 10, 2024, 07:42 AM  UpdatedAug 10, 2024, 10:06 AM  SAINT-DENIS, France - After enduring years of construction work on the Olympic Village opposite her block of flats, 15-year-old schoolgirl Enda Fofana had hoped for a free ticket to see the Paris 2024 Games.\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 391, \"end\": 398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"REUTERS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 477, \"end\": 483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9997214369068788, \"rank\": 0.0002782641944682141, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 535, \"end\": 550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.372229418665799e-24, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It never materialised.\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The teenager lives in Seine-Saint-Denis, a gritty, racially mixed suburb reaching north-east away from the capital, where the government and local mayors hope investment in new housing, sports facilities, metro lines and cycle lanes will leave a lasting legacy of urban and economic renewal.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 718, \"end\": 735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games' organisers pledged that Seine-Saint-Denis would be a pulsating focal point of the Paris Olympics, home to the athletes' village, the Stade de France national stadium and a new 5,000-seat aquatics centre.\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1024, \"end\": 1041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Ms Fofana echoed the sentiment of some in the area who complained that Paris 2024 did too little to help them enjoy the Games first hand.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1280, \"end\": 1290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.959486562020256e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We thought they would plan things for us because, well, it's the Games, it's the biggest event in the world,\\\" Ms Fofana said.\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her flat's balcony overlooks the entrance to the Olympic village, her middle school nestled among the buildings.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr David Lebon, a senior official in the Saint-Denis town hall said all students from Ms Fofana's middle school had received an invitation to a sporting event, and she and her friends took part in the torch relay.\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1593, \"end\": 1604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Leb\\u00f3n\", \"score\": 0.9999939563854969, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Lebon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Leb\\u00f3n\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Leb\\u00f3n\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her mother, Ms Ketty Choux-Fofana, said she never saw the invite.\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She added there had been joyful moments during the Games but cited inconveniences too: longer work commutes because of snarled local roads, heightened police checks and athletes partying under their windows as the Games wound up.\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 2100, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another Saint-Denis resident, Ms Betty Bonheur, expressed disappointment that tickets were unaffordable to many residents in Seine-Saint-Denis, the poorest of mainland France's administrative departments where the unemployment rate is nearly 50 per cent higher than the national average.\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2135, \"end\": 2140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betty_Suarez\", \"score\": 0.9000780451880667, \"rank\": 0.07790055995472447, \"text\": \"Betty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betty_Suarez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betty_Suarez\"}, {\"begin\": 2270, \"end\": 2276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9997214369068788, \"rank\": 0.0002782641944682141, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would have liked them to say 'Here, we have got tickets, we can give you some', to get people involved, to allocate cheaper tickets.\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2526, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That wasn't the case,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A Saint-Denis town hall spokesperson said a total of 10,000 opening ceremony invites and 9,000 invites for sports events at the Olympics and Paralympics had been offered to the town's 114,000 people.\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Amine Ben Dziri said his daughter was among those fortunate to receive a ticket.\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She triumphed in a school competition and won a ticket to the athletics.\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2918, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was her first time in such a big stadium.\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2965, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was very nice,\\\" he told Reuters in a local park that had been transformed into a free-to-enter fan zone that was half-full.\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 3092, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2993, \"end\": 3000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.737490948447508e-14, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games have delighted vast, jubilant crowds with sporting events held among some of the capital's most famous landmarks including the Place de la Concorde, Eiffel Tower and Grand Palais - the picture-perfect version of Paris that can seem distant from the hard-knock streets of Saint-Denis.\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3316, \"end\": 3321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0243131133850608e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Local officials hope that the Games will have delivered a jolt to the local economy.\", \"from\": 3389, \"to\": 3473, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Village that has been home to some 10,500 athletes will be transformed into housing units, including social and student housing.\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3478, \"end\": 3493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.372229418665799e-24, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two of the three new developments the Games will leave behind are located in Seine-Saint-Denis.\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3693, \"end\": 3710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But some residents told Reuters they questioned the sustainability of wider economic benefits.\", \"from\": 3713, \"to\": 3807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3737, \"end\": 3744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.737490948447508e-14, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Mohammed Ydriss Smaali, 21, said he felt the government and local authorities had missed an opportunity to develop job prospects in the area.\", \"from\": 3809, \"to\": 3953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Lots of jobs have been created, even if it was only in the short term,\\\" said Mr Smaali.\", \"from\": 3955, \"to\": 4043, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But no-one did anything, for example, to prioritise the people, the young people who live here.\\\"\", \"from\": 4044, \"to\": 4141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"REUTERS  France  Olympics 2024  Global economy  E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Personal Data Protection Notice  Need help?\", \"from\": 4142, \"to\": 4305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4142, \"end\": 4149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"REUTERS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 4151, \"end\": 4157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9997214369068788, \"rank\": 0.0002782641944682141, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 4222, \"end\": 4230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RSS Feed\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach us here.\", \"from\": 4306, \"to\": 4320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertise with us\", \"from\": 4322, \"to\": 4339, \"entities\": []}]}"